main.desc:
I am a small discord bot created by [Aidan#8883](https://discordapp.com/users/384439774972215296/) for his server that now anyone can use!

[Aidan's Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/c/AidanMapper)  |  [Aidan's Discord Server](https://discord.gg/KXrDUZfBpq)  |  Invite me (Click profile)
